pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "#191919"
elements:
- elementId: shape_header
  elementType: shape
  bounds: [40, 40, 40, 40]
  opacity: 0.2
  shapeName: rect
  fill:
    type: solid
    color: "#6366F133"
- elementId: text_title
  elementType: text
  bounds: [90, 40, 700, 40]
  content:
    align: [left, middle]
    fontSize: 28
    fontFamily: "Liter"
    color: "#EFEFEF"
    text: |
      <p><strong>Cross-modal Fusion: audio + video</strong></p>
- elementId: shape_line
  elementType: shape
  bounds: [40, 90, 1200, 2]
  shapeName: rect
  fill:
    type: solid
    color: "#6366F1"
- elementId: text_content
  elementType: text
  bounds: [40, 120, 580, 520]
  content:
    align: [left, top]
    fontSize: 16
    fontFamily: "微软雅黑"
    color: "#CCCCCC"
    lineHeight: 1.5
    text: |
      <p><strong style="color:#6366F1">Архитектура фьюжна</strong></p>
      <p></p>
      <p>1. <strong>Аудио как триггер</strong> (always-on)</p>
      <p>   - VAD + Onset Detection</p>
      <p>   - MFCC + ZCR + Spectral Centroid</p>
      <p></p>
      <p>2. <strong>Видео как валидатор</strong> (sleep mode)</p>
      <p>   - MediaPipe Hands (21 keypoints)</p>
      <p>   - Optical Flow для свайпов</p>
      <p>   - Камера просыпается по аудио</p>
      <p></p>
      <p>3. <strong>Late Fusion Layer</strong></p>
      <p>   - Score multiply / lightweight MLP</p>
      <p>   - Threshold = 0.6</p>
      <p></p>
      <p>4. <strong>Device Router</strong></p>
      <p>   - Lamp / Cond. / Curt. / TV / Lock</p>
- elementId: shape_box
  elementType: shape
  bounds: [660, 120, 580, 520]
  shapeName: rect
  fill:
    type: solid
    color: "#262626"
  border:
    style: solid
    width: 1
    color: "#333333"
- elementId: text_rdf
  elementType: text
  bounds: [680, 140, 540, 480]
  content:
    align: [left, top]
    fontSize: 14
    fontFamily: "微软雅黑"
    color: "#CCCCCC"
    lineHeight: 1.4
    text: |
      <p><strong style="color:#6366F1">RDF-граф знаний (rdflib)</strong></p>
      <p></p>
      <p>- <strong>Классы:</strong> AudioCommand, VideoGesture,</p>
      <p>  IoTDevice, GestureType, Intent, Slot, Speaker</p>
      <p></p>
      <p>- <strong>Свойства:</strong></p>
      <p>  hasDevice, hasGestureType, hasIntent,</p>
      <p>  hasSlot, performedBy, correspondsTo</p>
      <p></p>
      <p>- <strong>Кросс-модальные связи:</strong></p>
      <p>  audio_001 ↔ video_001 (same speaker + device)</p>
      <p></p>
      <p>- <strong>SPARQL-запросы:</strong></p>
      <p>  — Команды по устройству</p>
      <p>  — Cross-modal пары</p>
      <p>  — Распределение интентов</p>
      <p>  — Типы жестов</p>
      <p></p>
      <p>- <strong>Форматы:</strong> Turtle (.ttl), RDF/XML (.rdf)</p>
